Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.77,0:01:13.51,Caption,,0000,0000,0000,,For a new Japan\NVote Pooch
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.38,0:01:18.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Corruption upon corruption.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.72,0:01:21.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What has Japan come to?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.97,0:01:23.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's why you're here,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.02,0:01:25.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to change things like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.77,0:01:27.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.48,0:01:29.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The results of the election are in!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.59,0:01:34.74,Caption,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnBuffaloStance\c&H000000&\bord0\frz18.771\fscx111.25\fscy145\pos(109,132)}Pooch: zero votes
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.59,0:01:34.74,Caption,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnBuffaloStance\c&H000000&\bord0\frz18.771\fscx111.25\fscy145\pos(325,281)}Sucks\Nto be\Nyou!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.52,0:01:32.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, how big was the margin?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.03,0:01:34.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We lost with zero votes!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.94,0:01:36.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.53,0:01:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I've been thinking so much about Japan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.07,0:01:42.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why? Why? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.58,0:01:45.95,Caption,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H000003&\3c&HFFFFFF&\bord2\move(319,10,307,325,)}Because you're a dog...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.95,0:01:47.16,Caption,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H000003&\3c&HFFFFFF&\pos(307,325)\bord2}Because you're a dog...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.95,0:01:47.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe because you're a dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.46,0:01:56.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was live at the electoral \Nheadquarters of the Canine Party
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.34,0:01:59.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't hunt our hair! You won't hunt it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.39,0:02:01.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't hunt it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.64,0:02:05.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! You did rather well.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.35,0:02:06.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was kinda nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.73,0:02:08.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you gonna keep ignoring him?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.48,0:02:12.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Soda! Give him soda!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.82,0:02:16.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss! Boss! Hang on, Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.74,0:02:21.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pierre! Pierre!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.12,0:02:26.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.70,0:02:27.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And who's this 'Pierre'?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.12,0:02:30.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give him some more!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.30,0:02:37.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don Patch!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.71,0:02:38.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.63,0:02:41.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! My hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.39,0:02:46.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My precious hat\Nmy mommy gave me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.60,0:02:48.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're all so mean to hide it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.10,0:02:50.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss! Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.94,0:02:52.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Wig Gang!\N- Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.06,0:02:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're being really rude, you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.19,0:02:56.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not one of these Wigs.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.44,0:02:59.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What!? Then who are you!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.99,0:03:01.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean you can't tell just by looking?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.36,0:03:03.91,Caption,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFF0804&\3c&HFCFCFF&\fad(100,0)}That's why he's stuck here...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.70,0:03:03.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.12,0:03:06.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Boss!\N- Boss! Come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.29,0:03:09.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss, you're not a hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.71,0:03:12.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What!? You mean I'm not a hat!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.71,0:03:14.71,Caption,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26}Note: In Japanese, the sound a "higurashi," a species of cicada, makes is "tsuku-boushi." "Boushi" is also the word for hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.75,0:03:16.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chirp, hat...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.17,0:03:17.71,Caption,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFF2071&\3c&HFFFFFF&\move(2,369,447,367)\}He's not a hat...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.71,0:03:18.30,Caption,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFF2071&\3c&HFFFFFF&\move(447,367,600,0)\}He's not a hat...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.75,0:03:18.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chirp, hat...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.17,0:03:24.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, you sure are something.\NYou really had me thinking
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.97,0:03:29.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was actually your hat.\NYou're a high level hajikelist.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.85,0:03:32.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Interesting!\NI challenge you to a Hajike Duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.19,0:03:34.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-Sure, if you wanna.\N- Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.98,0:03:36.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case,\Nlet's duel with the expert rules!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.58,0:04:38.67,Narrator-ish,,0000,0000,0000,,The Expert Rules:
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.96,0:04:43.42,Narrator-ish,,0000,0000,0000,,A special set of rules for\Nhigh-level Hajikelists.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.72,0:04:47.01,Narrator-ish,,0000,0000,0000,,The rules are to go crazy\Nusing a common theme.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.10,0:04:50.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss's definitely gonna Hajike!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.43,0:04:51.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's over for this guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.64,0:04:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The theme will be...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.10,0:04:57.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The theme...
