Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.05,0:06:11.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's cold... freezing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.68,0:06:16.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't go back home\N'til I've sold all of them. What can I do?
