Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.95,0:07:19.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So please buy some fish sticks!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.62,0:07:22.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Buy them... then eat them!
