Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.02,0:09:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's sad! That is way too sad!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.74,0:09:17.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I can't believe it!\NThat shouldn't happen on Christmas!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.45,0:09:20.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he answered wrong!\NBy a long shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.83,0:09:23.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say it isn't true!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.95,0:09:26.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I could tell you it isn't true!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.50,0:09:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.13,0:09:30.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So very true!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.72,0:09:38.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't win...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.55,0:09:40.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.10,0:09:43.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hang on, Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.52,0:09:46.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don Patch!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.98,0:09:50.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For you to reveal such a sad past,\Nyou're quite the Hajikelist.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.73,0:09:54.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case,\NI'll give it all I've got!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.11,0:09:56.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss's so determined!
