Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.06,0:10:32.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's lost it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.86,0:10:36.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Screw the Hajike Duel! I'm gonna kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.86,0:10:37.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure-killing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.61,0:10:41.28,Villains,,0000,0000,0000,,Don Patch Shuriken Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.41,0:10:46.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cry! Cry!\NBurst into tears!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.12,0:10:53.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weird... Bo-bobo ought to\Nbe dodging the attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.17,0:10:58.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How bizarre! It's not supposed to...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.80,0:11:03.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I told you you weren't ready\Nto pilot Bo-bobo yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.85,0:11:06.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! I can do\Nthis just fine!
