Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.52,0:11:16.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Docking!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.49,0:11:21.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah? What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.32,0:11:23.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to me, Aircraft #1!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.58,0:11:27.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aircraft #2!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.21,0:11:31.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aircraft #3!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.04,0:11:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aircraft #4!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.83,0:11:36.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Formation...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.71,0:11:41.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Assemble!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.14,0:11:46.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Assembling complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.89,0:11:52.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How is this an assembly!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.27,0:11:54.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That combo is so not fair, oink!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.48,0:11:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to parts 1 and 2?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.19,0:11:58.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naw, that combo's cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.94,0:12:02.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This technique...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.49,0:12:04.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me play too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.91,0:12:07.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.70,0:12:10.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.95,0:12:12.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's gonna end like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.00,0:12:16.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So... who's that Wig Gang\Nyou were talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.71,0:12:21.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're villains that torture the people of Hajike Village with the Hair Hunt.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.92,0:12:23.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that means...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.30,0:12:26.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bo-bobo, this village has been\Nattacked by the Hair Hunters too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.18,0:12:33.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me go! Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.88,0:13:01.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a nice head of hair!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.51,0:13:04.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss! It's Wig Gang!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.55,0:13:06.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's H-block's Deputy Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.78,0:13:09.72,Caption,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(315,270)\bord2}H-Block Deputy Captain: Tarashi
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.55,0:13:09.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's H-Block's Tarashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.22,0:13:11.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.93,0:13:17.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You picked the wrong day to mess with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.73,0:13:23.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bo-bobo, save me! Bo-bobo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.53,0:13:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He ignored me--!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.83,0:13:33.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I blossomed!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.79,0:13:34.29,Caption,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs28}Note: This is a pun on saying "He left."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.29,0:13:37.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you've finally blossomed!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.34,0:13:42.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-He blossomed!\N-He blossomed!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.71,0:13:45.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-He blossomed!\N-He blossomed!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.18,0:13:53.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Curses! No one ignores me and gets away with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.64,0:13:55.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This means war!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.10,0:13:59.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna break into their base and kick their asses right? Let's do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.31,0:14:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I must do this alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.19,0:14:02.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.69,0:14:05.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you guys are weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.82,0:14:06.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weak...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.74,0:14:10.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.41,0:14:14.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, I'll go with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.21,0:14:18.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He blossomed even more!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.12,0:14:21.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Wig Gang is part of\Nthe Hair Hunters.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.17,0:14:25.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a good enough reason for\Nme to beat the crap out of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.30,0:14:30.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This man and I share the same fate.\NIn that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.22,0:14:34.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His fate is to...\Nbecome my ally.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.64,0:14:36.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Follow me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.43,0:14:37.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Floral attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.60,0:14:40.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Floral attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.81,0:14:41.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Floral attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.27,0:14:43.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's good!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.65,0:14:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The two greatest Hajikelists\Nteaming up together...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.07,0:14:51.57,Caption,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx93.75\fscy101.25\pos(325,257)\fad(100,0)}Hair Hunter Brigade  H-Block Base (Wig Gang)
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.83,0:14:56.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, how 'bout that winter uniform?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.16,0:14:59.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know, right?\NWith those cute little white boots...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.71,0:15:04.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that noise?
