Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.43,0:15:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Office lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.72,0:15:14.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.72,0:15:19.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am office layayaya-dy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.89,0:15:23.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, good.\NNow, let's move on to lesson two.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.23,0:15:27.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I don't learn English,\NI'll never get a good job.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.15,0:15:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a bad day!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.86,0:15:31.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, it's coming this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.82,0:15:34.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reinforce our defenses!
