Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.26,0:15:51.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you guys wear wigs?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.47,0:15:53.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Block is very fashion-conscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.59,0:15:57.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So we get special\Nauthorization to wear wigs.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.22,0:16:00.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's why they call you the "Wig Gang."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.10,0:16:04.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As you can see, we get tons\Nof love letters.
