Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.24,0:16:20.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What have you done with Beauty?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.45,0:16:22.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hell if we know!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.58,0:16:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll kill you!
