Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.71,0:16:32.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A'ight, good distraction!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.76,0:16:35.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna Hajike our asses off!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.73,0:16:51.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These guys are strong...\NToo strong...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.82,0:17:00.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, well, well, look who it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.87,0:17:03.71,Caption,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(317,275)}H-Block Captain: Maitel
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.54,0:17:03.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What business do you have here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.50,0:17:06.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're the gang leader?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.09,0:17:12.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.59,0:17:15.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you heard of Medusa?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.34,0:17:20.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Greek monster who could\Nturn you to stone with a single glance.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.89,0:17:22.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Don't tell me--
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.02,0:17:24.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.35,0:17:26.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have the eyes of the Medusa!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.48,0:17:30.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.27,0:17:33.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm turning to stone!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.24,0:17:36.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.66,0:17:39.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.24,0:17:43.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- I'm turning into a carrot!\N- What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.58,0:17:51.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't you just a carrot!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.88,0:17:52.34,Sound Effects,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H00FCFF&\pos(231,55)\i1\fscx200\fscy100\t(\fscx100\fscy100)\bord5\frz3.712}Eh--------!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.30,0:17:54.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,*Stare*
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.51,0:17:57.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I turned into a cabbage!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.80,0:17:59.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why couldn't I be lettuce!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.97,0:18:00.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't screw with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.64,0:18:03.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.14,0:18:09.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I'm still changing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.40,0:18:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Slow down, the beach isn't going anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.57,0:18:16.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And don't you try to catch me,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.57,0:18:17.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or else I'll run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.20,0:18:21.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I turned back into a carrot!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.53,0:18:25.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How the hell did you turn into a carrot!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.25,0:18:32.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No good. I can't beat him as a cabbage.
