Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.38,0:21:20.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, get over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.00,0:21:22.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a moment, dear. I'm coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.26,0:21:29.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.47,0:21:31.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're leaving!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.10,0:21:33.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe you!
